README : zephyr

    let HTCondor soar to the cloud

DESCRIPTION
    
    zephyr is service that automagically provisions cloud-based 
    computing resources to augment the existing, fixed resources 
    of an HTCondor batch system based on user job demand.

STATUS

    prototyping

OPTIONS

USAGE

NOTES

